questions.question:
What will this code output?

```php
function test() {
    return 5;
    echo "Done";
}
echo test();
```

What is the output of this code?

```php
$x = 10;
$func = function() use ($x) {
    return $x;
};
$x = 20;
echo $func();
```

What will this code output with strict_types=1?

```php
declare(strict_types=1);
function add(int $a, int $b) {
    return $a + $b;
}
echo add(2.5, 3);
```

What will this code output?

```php
function &getValue() {
    $val = 10;
    return $val;
}
$ref = &getValue();
$ref = 20;
echo $val;
```

What is the result of this code?

```php
function calc($a, $b = 2, $c = 3) {
    return $a + $b + $c;
}
echo calc(5, c: 10);
```
